text: Eteke mucha'i yetiya ubhayara satrauka dharaiba khujile, tetiya se'i byaktiye cinamrai ka’ba dharaile, ‘he mucha! Yoraa kali tumi yenekai ejana byaktika hatya karaicha, tenekai moko hatya karaiba khujicha neki? Arasye tumi prthiraira bukuta sbecchacarai ha’ba bicaraicha, arau tumi santi sthapanakarai sakalara antarbhukta ha’ba nibicaraa’
